narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Great overview of the various types of jazz and jazz history.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: The quizzes are very time-consuming and really require focus while reading the assigned articles. However, having the option to resubmit every assignment takes the pressure off tremendously. There are no tests and all the essays are straight from the lecture (which are thankfully recorded).

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes! Prof Duffy's enthusiasm is infectious and being able to resubmit all the assignments is amazing. I only warn that the HW quizzes can take a long time because some of the assigned passages are very long.

narratives.question_text: The Canvas course site allowed me to identify and access required course materials easily.
